snippet.description:

LYRICS
Putting on a drum show.
 
Completed checklist for today,
Now they have to let you out of your cage,
Feeling stuck between a rock and a home,
Two places you do not want to go, so, so.
 
He’s putting on a drum show,
Even now, even now,
He’ll take the longer way home,
Even now, even now,
He’ll never, ever say so,
He drives fast just to feel it, feel it,
He drives slow if his song’s not over,
Drown it out, drown it out.
 
He’d rather feel something than nothing at all,
So he swerves all around as his head starts to fall,
Turns it up,
Stuck between a rock and a home,
Two places he does not want to go, so, so.
 
I’ve been this way,
I want to change.

snippet.title: Good Boy - Official Trailer (2025) Shane Jensen, Arielle Friedman, Larry Fessenden
snippet.description:
Check out the creepy trailer for GOOD BOY, an upcoming horror thriller movie starring Indy the Dog, Shane Jensen, Arielle Friedman, and Larry Fessenden.

Our canine hero, Indy, finds himself on a new adventure with his human owner—and best friend—Todd, leaving city life for a long-vacant family home in the country. From the start, two things are abundantly clear: Indy is wary of the creepy old house, and his affection for Todd is unwavering. After moving in, Indy is immediately vexed by empty corners, tracks an invisible presence only he can see, perceives phantasmagoric warnings from a long-dead dog, and is haunted by visions of the previous occupant’s grim death. When Todd begins succumbing to the dark forces swirling around the house, Indy must battle a malevolence intent on dragging his beloved Todd into the afterlife.

Good Boy is produced by Ben Leonberg and Kari Fischer. It is written by Alex Cannon and Ben Leonberg.

Good Boy, directed by Ben Leonberg, opens in North American theaters on October 3, 2025 and opens in the UK on October 10, 2025.

#GoodBoy #Movies #IGN

snippet.title: Vicente Fernández - Un Millón de Primaveras (Letra)
snippet.description:
Vicente Fernández - Un Millón de Primaveras (Letra / Lyrics)
Vicente Fernández - Un Millón de Primaveras (Con Letra / Lyrics)
Vicente Fernández - Un Millón de Primaveras (Subtitulada en Español / Lyrics)
Vicente Fernández - Un Millón de Primaveras (Lyrics)

¿Y si digo que es una de las mejores canciones jamás creadas? Gracias Joan Sebastian por tan grande letra y grande Chente por esta interpretación 🧡🍐

"Un Millón de Primaveras" escrita por Joan Sebastian y popularizada por Vicente Fernández, habla sobre el dolor de la pérdida de un ser querido, específicamente un hijo, y el proceso de duelo del padre, quien habla con su hijo fallecido, prometiéndole que, aunque le costará un millón de primaveras olvidarlo, eventualmente lo hará.

→ Sigue escuchando "Un Millón de Primaveras":
https://open.spotify.com/track/6j5LtifAnuTjTYvml61yFZ?si=017f5f49a6654c2e

→ Lyrics:
[Letra de "Millón de Primaveras"]

[Verso 1]
Te molesta si te hablo de mi amor
Y me pides, por favor, olvide el tema
Y que cambie la letra de mis canciones
Y tu nombre quite ya de aquel poema
Te molesta; aguanta, por favor
Te lo juro, estoy a punto de olvidarte

[Coro]
Solo falta un millón de primaveras
Unos cuantos siglos solo he de adorarte
Solo falta un millón de primaveras
Después de eso ya no vuelvo a molestarte
Oh no, no volveré a cantarte
Si te molesta, si te molesta

[Verso 2]
Te molesta el perro que ladró
De alegría, anunciando tu llegada
Y me dices que ese perro está loco
Que le ladra a la persona equivocada
Yo te digo: "Por favor, aguanta un poco"
"Ten paciencia, no le des otra pedrada"
Oh no, no volverá a ladrarte
Si te molesta, si te molesta

[Coro]
Solo falta un millón de primaveras
Unos cuantos siglos solo he de adorarte
Solo falta un millón de primaveras
Después de eso ya no vuelvo a molestarte
Oh no, no volveré a cantarte
Si te molesta, si te molesta

[Outro]
Si te molesta, si te molesta

#VicenteFernandez #UnMillonDePrimaveras #LetrasLyrics #RegionalMexicano

Espero les haya encantado el vídeo, gracias a todos por ver y apoyar mi contenido, recuerden beber agua y respirar aire, los quiero mucho ♥

🎤 Letra / Lyrics: Romeo Santos - Llévame Contigo

[Letra de "Llévame Contigo"]

[Intro]
Hey, escucha las palabras de Romeo

[Verso 1]
No sé si has cambiado de opinión y no te vas
Si tu vuelo de las 3 cancelarás
¿Cómo mi invento arte de magia?
¿Cómo logro que me ames mucho más?
Sé que tal vez no lo digas pero me ves un llorón
Y ese maldito viaje ya se confirmó
Solo recuerda, si me dejas no se vale
Te sugiero por favor

[Coro]
Llévame contigo, que no aguanto la aflicción
Llévame contigo, no seas malita y no, no, no, oh-oh, oh-oh
Llévame contigo, y si te vas de vacación
Llévame contigo, aunque sea de chaperón
Llévame contigo o habrá desolación
Llévame contigo, pónle fin a mi temor
¿Donde se fue tu amor? Para buscarlo rápido

[Interludio]
Come on
You know who's the best [?]
The King
Copy?

[Verso 2]
Para ti, "Hasta siempre te amaré" fue un refrán
Y el matrimonio un papel que romperás
Si es que acaso queda un poco 'e cariñito
Regaládme tu amistad
Please, please

[Coro]
Llévame contigo, que no aguanto la aflicción
Llévame contigo, no seas malita y no, no, no, oh-oh, oh-oh
Llévame contigo, y si te vas de vacación
Llévame contigo, aunque sea de chaperón
Llévame contigo o habrá desolación
Llévame contigo, pónle fin a mi temor
¿Donde se fue tu amor? Para buscarlo rápido

[Interludio]
Llora guitarra, llora
Dale mami
Está bien [?]

[Outro]
Take me with you tomorrow
Take me and I won't bother
Take me with you tomorrow
Take me and I won't bother
Take me, take me, take me
Take me, take me with you
Tomorrow, tomorrow
Tomorrow, tomorrow, tomorrow
You need this in your life
Tomorrow, tomorrow

snippet.description:

Stream new music from Hayley Williams: https://bio.to/hayleywilliams

Follow Hayley Williams:
http://hayleywilliams.net
https://www.instagram.com/yelyahwilliams
https://www.facebook.com/hayleywilliams/

CREDITS:
Director - AJ Gibboney & Zac Farro
Producer - Robert H. Dyar Jr
DP - Nyk Allen
Prod Co - Creative Team Studios
Editor - AJ Gibboney
Color - Cameron Marygold
VFX - Brainchild 
1st AC - James Tentity

Steady - Daniel Vorlet

BBE - Luke Lamar
BBG - Patrick Strunk

Art Lead - Kristen Jordan
PA - Kennedy Martin
PA - Jackson Hubbard

Shot on 35mm Kodak film 🌟

LYRICS:
In the wake of your sunshine 
I’ve never felt so glum
Think I’m made up of moonlight
Don’t reach quite as far 
But I still show up

Stick around for someone
Stick around til dawn 
I wonder

Do you ever feel so alone
You could implode and no one would know?
And when you look around and nobody’s home
Don’t you wanna go back
To wherever we’re from? 
Wherever we’re from

Spaced out at a stop light
Who’s layin’ on their horn? 
Cause it’s in tune with this song
Wanna put it in park
And listen all day long 
Hey man, roll down your window
Light’s already yellow
I wonder 

Do you ever feel so alone
That you could implode and no one would know?
And when you look around and nobody’s home
Don’t you wanna go back
To wherever we’re from? 
Wherever we’re from


On my way to 37 years 
I do not know if I’ll ever know
What in the living fuck I’m doing here
Does anyone know if this is normal? 
I wonder
I wonder 

Do you ever feel so alone
That you could implode and no one would know?
And when you look around and nobodies home
Don’t you wanna go back
To wherever we’re from? 
Wherever we’re from

In the wake of of your sunshine
I’ve never felt so glum

#HayleyWilliams #Glum

snippet.title: Rao Bahadur | Teaser | Satya Dev | Venkatesh Maha | GMB | SriChakraas | A+S | Summer 2026
snippet.description:
Rao Bahadur is a psychological drama set against the backdrop of a fading aristocracy - Made in Telugu, for the world.
 
Directed by acclaimed filmmaker Venkatesh Maha and starring the versatile Satya Dev as Rao Bahadur, the film is presented by Superstar Mahesh Babu & Namrata Shirodkar’s GMB Entertainment and produced by A+S Movies and SriChakraas Entertainments.
 
Releasing Summer 2026, in Theaters worldwide.
 
Genre - Psychological Drama, Suspense, Dark Comedy, Magical Realism.
 
 
Cast and Crew Details:

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunning (I AM CHEATING)
snippet.description:
Minecraft Speedrunning (I AM CHEATING)

DISCLAIMER: I am CHEATING! (Technically)

I am using mods that are not allowed in official leaderboard speedruns. This is practice for my videos, not for world records! I am also simulating ender eye calculation using a mod, I am only throwing the eyes to simulate a time spend, as official speedrunners use a bot to calculate the stronghold location off of 1/2 ender eyes.

I am also using no fog, optifine zoom, increased pearl rates (matching 1.16 rates), and a custom f3 menu with Nether Coordinates. (And maybe more, idk, who cares)

I can still remember me and Miss November Rain
Beautiful and strange
Always so inclined, coloring outside the lines
Yeah, you were never on time

You've always been slightly awkward, kind of weird
Upside down and not all here
What's wrong with me and you is crystal clear

[Chorus]
Sometimes I'm in a room where I don't belong
And the house is on fire and there's no alarm
And the walls are melting too
How 'bout you?
I've never been the favorite, thought I'd seen it all
'Til I got my invitation to the lunatic ball
And my friends are comin' too
How 'bout you?
Don't worry, it's all just a symptom of being human

Unpack all your baggage, hide it in the attic, where
You hope it disappears
This all seems so familiar, but it doesn't feel like home
It's just another unknown

You've always been slightly awkward, kind of weird
Upside down and not all here
Right or wrong, it's all so crystal clear

And the walls are melting too
How 'bout you?

How 'bout you?

We're all just passin' through
Passengers on a ship of fools
